@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_limvfa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.09
    v0 = wp.cos((v1 * v0))
    v0 = ((0.37 - wp.sin(tmp + 0.06)) / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.54) + (v0 + 0.04 / v0 + 0.79)))
    v0 = v0
    v2 = 0.44
    v2 = 0.74
    tmp = 0.72
    data[tid] = v0
